This paper focuses on Natural Language Processing (NLP) and emotion analysis, which falls under the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also proposes two new tasks based on the dataset, which involve machine learning and inference, indicating a potential fit for Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also involves statistical analysis, which could fall under Information Retrieval (cs.IR) or Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories.
